STATE of Iowa, Appellee,
v.
Kathy Jo PERRY, Appellant. No. 18-0351 Supreme Court of Iowa. Filed April 26, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

A defendant appeals the sentence imposed following her conviction for driving while her license was barred. DECISION OF COURT OF APPEALS VACATED; SENTENCE VACATED IN PART AND CASE REMANDED.

DECISION OF COURT OF APPEALS VACATED. SENTENCE VACATED IN PART. CASE REMANDED.
